OL,3,CChildren break record for largest
OL,4,Creading lesson
OL,6,FThousands of children in Portsmouth
OL,7,Fhave broken a Guinness World Record
OL,8,Fafter taking part in a mass reading
OL,9,Flesson.
OL,11,FThe pupils set a new record for the
OL,12,Fworld's largest reading lesson across
OL,13,Fmultiple venues, surpassing the
OL,14,Fprevious record of 3,509 participants,
OL,15,Fset by Eastbourne Area Secondary
OL,16,FSchools in 2014.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
