OL,3,CChildren break record for largest
OL,4,Creading lesson
OL,6,FThe event was organised by groups
OL,7,Fincluding Portsmouth Creates,
OL,8,FPortsmouth Football Club, Pompey in
OL,9,Fthe Community and Portsmouth Library
OL,10,FServices. It was hosted by Blue Peter
OL,11,Fpresenter Abby Cook.
OL,13,FAt Fratton Park, a 35-minute lesson
OL,14,Fwas led by local retired headteacher
OL,15,FHoward Payne, alongside author, Dan
OL,16,FFreedman, as well as Clare Martin MBE,
OL,17,FCEO of Pompey in the Community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
