CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772798583
OL,3,CChildren break record for largest
OL,4,Creading lesson
OL,6,FDan Freedman read from his book I Am
OL,7,FLenny Brown, and afterwards pupils
OL,8,Fwere encouraged to reflect on its
OL,9,Fthemes and discuss the characters.
OL,11,FMany of the children arrived dressed
OL,12,Fin their favourite World Book Day
OL,13,Fcostumes.
OL,15,FDavid Hayman, Campaign Director for
OL,16,Fthe National Year of Reading, said:
OL,17,F"It's great to see Portsmouth going
OL,18,Fall in to bring reading to life for
OL,19,Fchildren this World Book Day and even
OL,20,Fsetting new Guinness World Records."
OL,26,@yD@AOU
