PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772798583
OL,3,CChildren break record for largest
OL,4,Creading lesson
OL,6,F"Football acts as a powerful gateway
OL,7,Fto reading for a lot of people and, if
OL,8,Fyou meet children where they are and
OL,9,Ftap into their passions, we can show
OL,10,Fthem that reading is the ultimate tool
OL,11,Fto get more out of the things they
OL,12,Falready love."
OL,14,FDuring the challenge, stewards
OL,15,Fsubmitted attendance verification
OL,16,Fforms while independent timekeepers
OL,17,Fconfirmed the duration of the lesson
OL,18,Fahead of the official Guinness World
OL,19,FRecords adjudication.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
