CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772798583
OL,3,CChildren break record for largest
OL,4,Creading lesson
OL,6,FThe documentation was then reviewed by
OL,7,Fthe Guinness World Records adjudicator
OL,8,Fbefore the final result was announced.
OL,10,FAndrew Cullen, Chief Executive Officer
OL,11,Fat Portsmouth Football Club, said:
OL,12,F"This was truly a day to remember and
OL,13,Fa historic moment for the city.
OL,15,F"Portsmouth FC proudly sits at the
OL,16,Fheart of the community, and it was
OL,17,Ffantastic to see the power of
OL,18,Fpartnership across the city and what
OL,19,Fcan be achieved when organisations
OL,20,Fwork together to create life-changing
OL,21,Fopportunities."
OL,26,@tD@AOU}D@OO]
